(105, 1, '2013-05-05 13:43:37', '2013-05-05 13:43:37', '<h2>Financing</h2>\r\nClimate Select from GE Money is a financing solution to help homeowners get the HVAC products they want to enhance their home’s comfort and value.\r\n\r\nThrough the Climate Select network of participating dealers, GE Money offers flexible consumer lending options for furnaces, central air conditioners, fireplaces, ventilation systems, hot water heaters, humidifiers, stoves and more.\r\n\r\n<img alt="Air Conditioning systems financing" src="http://www.1responsehvac.com/images/just-cs-logo.gif" width="233" height="80" /><img alt="Heating systems financing" src="http://www.1responsehvac.com/images/cs-image.jpg" width="200" height="165" />\r\n<div id="column1">\r\n<h2><strong>Leasing</strong></h2>\r\nOur leasing program is unique. We specialize in providing financing for projects that our competition simply can’t get done. We can finance the capital equipment you need to keep your business on the leading edge of technology and with state-of-the-art processes, we can do simple one-at-a-time equipment leases. We can create a Master Lease structure for multiple purchases with periodic draws, in addition, we specialize in providing funds to renovate your facilities! A modern facility designed to your specific needs will be a more productive and professional-looking place for you, your employees and your customers. What type of renovations can be leased? Here are some of the most common:\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>American Standard HVAC Systems</li>\r\n	<li>Building Controls</li>\r\n	<li>Refrigeration</li>\r\n	<li>Other Brands (at least 50% American Standard Air required)</li>\r\n	<li>Computer Related Items (Hardware &amp; Software)</li>\r\n	<li>Telecommunications Systems</li>\r\n	<li>Office Equipment/Furniture</li>\r\n	<li>Ice Makers</li>\r\n	<li>Lighting Retrofit</li>\r\n	<li>Interim Repair Costs on Old Equipment</li>\r\n	<li>All Engineering and Installation Costs</li>\r\n	<li>Extended Warranties and Maint